A file photo of the ANC flag. Supplied: Stephanie de Sakutin The African National Congress has claimed Ekurhuleni s first victory by retaining the position of Speaker at Tuesday s council meeting. ANC councillor Patricia Khumalo received 117 votes while the Democratic Alliance s Shado Shabangu got 106. There was one spoilt ballot. A total 224 ballots were cast. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Related Share on Facebook Share Share on Twitter Tweet Share on Google Plus Share